                "type": "math",
                "latex": "\\tan \\theta = \\frac{2cy_0}{b^2 - a^2 + y_0^2(1 - \\frac{a^2}{b^2})} = \\frac{2cy_0}{y_0^2 \\cdot \\frac{c^2}{b^2} - c^2}"
