                "type": "math",
                "latex": "\\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{x^2}{a^2}+\\frac{y^2}{b^2} &= 1 \\\\\n\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(\\frac{x^2}{a^2}+\\frac{y^2}{b^2}\\right) &= \\frac{d}{dx}(1) \\\\\n\\frac{2x}{a^2} + \\frac{2y}{b^2} \\cdot \\frac{dy}{dx} &= 0\n\\end{aligned}"
